{"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/093f/65e0/59_large.png?m=1615956453", "name": "random", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/093f/65e0/59_normal.png?m=1615956453", "title": "随想", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/random", "topics": 3785, "footer": "", "header": "有的时候，可以停下来找找灵感，然后再继续。", "title_alternative": "Random", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/093f/65e0/59_mini.png?m=1615956453", "stars": 1214, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 59, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 663698, "username": "ShikiSuen", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/ShikiSuen", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/796c/341e/663698_mini.png?m=1721402587", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/796c/341e/663698_normal.png?m=1721402587", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/796c/341e/663698_large.png?m=1721402587", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/796c/341e/663698_xlarge.png?m=1721402587", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/796c/341e/663698_xlarge.png?m=1721402587", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/796c/341e/663698_xlarge.png?m=1721402587", "created": 1700591445, "last_modified": 1721402587}, "last_reply_by": "sagaxu", "last_touched": 1721450447, "title": "观 windows 大面积蓝屏有感", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1058716", "created": 1721402519, "deleted": 0, "content": "假设有一天：所有 windows 电脑、win 服务器全部死机，我们的生活能有多大影响？ \r\n\r\n微信，支付宝，这些基础的 app 应该全失效了，很多机构（银行，发电厂，医院）也会直接停止工作。\r\n\r\n一下就回归了原始社会，而且比原始社会还要落后，很多被机器替代的工作全都会受影响。", "content_rendered": "<p>假设有一天：所有 windows 电脑、win 服务器全部死机，我们的生活能有多大影响？ </p>\n<p>微信，支付宝，这些基础的 app 应该全失效了，很多机构（银行，发电厂，医院）也会直接停止工作。</p>\n<p>一下就回归了原始社会，而且比原始社会还要落后，很多被机器替代的工作全都会受影响。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1721404146, "replies": 36, "id": 1058716}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1691642161", "name": "bb", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1691642161", "title": "宽带症候群", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb", "topics": 15819, "footer": "", "header": "网速很重要。比快更快。", "title_alternative": "Broadband Symptom Complex", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1691642161", "stars": 7449, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 108, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 560653, "username": "NIIIIIIIIIICE", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/NIIIIIIIIIICE", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d1b6/cfba/560653_mini.png?m=1717319368", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d1b6/cfba/560653_normal.png?m=1717319368", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d1b6/cfba/560653_large.png?m=1717319368", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d1b6/cfba/560653_xlarge.png?m=1717319368", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d1b6/cfba/560653_xlarge.png?m=1717319368", "created": 1635980254, "last_modified": 1717319368}, "last_reply_by": "8e47e42", "last_touched": 1721460249, "title": "继腾讯之后阿里云也要对公共 DNS 限速了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1058732", "created": 1721411076, "deleted": 0, "content": "![]( https://i.imgur.com/SpKb5rf.png) \r\n \r\n\r\n涉及产品\r\n\r\n公共 DNS 是面向所有互联网用户的全球公共递归域名解析服务，本次限速仅影响公共 DNS 免费版。\r\n\r\n影响用户\r\n\r\n接入公共 DNS 免费版的用户，包括 DoH 、DoT 和 UDP 、TCP 的接入方式。\r\n\r\n生效时间\r\n\r\n2024 年 9 月 30 日 24 时起\r\n\r\n通知内容\r\n\r\n由于产品升级，从 2024 年 9 月 30 日起，公共 DNS 将对免费的解析请求采取智能流量管控措施。公共 DNS 仍会致力于为广大免费用户提供高质量的基础递归解析服务，但在高并发解析场景，将对公共 DNS 免费流量按请求源 IP 进行请求并发数限制。该请求并发量上限并非固定阈值，具体限速值将根据网络负载状况和公共 DNS 的整体服务质量适时调整，以保证公共 DNS 整体服务的稳定性和使用体验。\r\n\r\n公共 DNS 免费版的适用范围\r\n\r\n免费版服务适用于个人终端低并发使用，如流量过高（即 DoH/DoT：单 IP 访问量超过 20QPS ，UDP/TCP 流量超过 2000bps ）将会触发限速策略。个人用户也可以接入付费版服务，付费版产品每月提供 1000 万次的免费 HTTP 解析流量资源包，可基本满足个人使用场景。", "content_rendered": "<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SpKb5rf.png\"/> </p>\n<p>涉及产品</p>\n<p>公共 DNS 是面向所有互联网用户的全球公共递归域名解析服务，本次限速仅影响公共 DNS 免费版。</p>\n<p>影响用户</p>\n<p>接入公共 DNS 免费版的用户，包括 DoH 、DoT 和 UDP 、TCP 的接入方式。</p>\n<p>生效时间</p>\n<p>2024 年 9 月 30 日 24 时起</p>\n<p>通知内容</p>\n<p>由于产品升级，从 2024 年 9 月 30 日起，公共 DNS 将对免费的解析请求采取智能流量管控措施。公共 DNS 仍会致力于为广大免费用户提供高质量的基础递归解析服务，但在高并发解析场景，将对公共 DNS 免费流量按请求源 IP 进行请求并发数限制。该请求并发量上限并非固定阈值，具体限速值将根据网络负载状况和公共 DNS 的整体服务质量适时调整，以保证公共 DNS 整体服务的稳定性和使用体验。</p>\n<p>公共 DNS 免费版的适用范围</p>\n<p>免费版服务适用于个人终端低并发使用，如流量过高（即 DoH/DoT：单 IP 访问量超过 20QPS ，UDP/TCP 流量超过 2000bps ）将会触发限速策略。个人用户也可以接入付费版服务，付费版产品每月提供 1000 万次的免费 HTTP 解析流量资源包，可基本满足个人使用场景。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1721411108, "replies": 36, "id": 1058732}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/7327/8a4a/113_large.png?m=1679004895", "name": "hongkong", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/7327/8a4a/113_normal.png?m=1679004895", "title": "香港", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/hongkong", "topics": 181, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Hong Kong", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/7327/8a4a/113_mini.png?m=1679004895", "stars": 271, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 113, "parent_node_name": "cn"}, "member": {"id": 484027, "username": "dufldylan1", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/dufldylan1", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0a689724d3ca045f642f47eff6ec7fba?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0a689724d3ca045f642f47eff6ec7fba?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0a689724d3ca045f642f47eff6ec7fba?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1587003385, "last_modified": 1587003385}, "last_reply_by": "idragonet", "last_touched": 1721462096, "title": "去香港旅行有什么值得体验/购买的东西吗", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1058746", "created": 1721439533, "deleted": 0, "content": "明天要去香港一周，大佬们有什么推荐的 美食/数码/服装/......的店推荐吗？\r\n